      "description": "Presented in showroom condition, this vehicle is a true collector's specimen. The exterior features a flawless factory finish, protected by a professional-grade ceramic coating that highlights the deep luster of the paint with zero stone chips, scratches, or swirl marks. Inside, the cabin remains in a 'time-capsule' state; the premium leather seats show no bolster wear, the dashboard is crack-free, and the original floor mats are pristine. Mechanically, it is beyond reproach, having been exclusively serviced at authorized dealerships with a full binder of maintenance records included. Every button, sensor, and electronic feature operates exactly as it did the day it rolled off the assembly line. Always garage-kept under a breathable cover and never driven in inclement weather, this car smells and drives like new. This is a rare opportunity to own a virtually new vehicle for the discerning enthusiast who accepts nothing less than perfection.",
